Description: Full-stack adaptive learning system implementing the Causal Intervention 
    Attention Mechanism (CIAM) for trustworthy visual recognition under domain shift.
    Provides information bottleneck optimization, causal inference, and hierarchical
    adaptive collaboration. Includes replication scripts for MICCAI 2025 paper results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/CIAM-Lab/AdaptVisR
